
Design Name
===========
    TOP

Scan Style
==========
    muxed_scan
Design has a valid DFT rule check status

Global Constraints
==================
    Minimum number of scan chains: 44
    Maximum length of scan chains: no_value
    Lock-up element type: preferred_level_sensitive
    Mix clock edges in scan chain: false
    Prefix for unnamed scan objects: DFT_

Test signal objects
===================
    shift_enable: 
          object name: ScanEnable 
          pin name: ScanEnable 
          hookup_pin: ScanEnable 
          hookup_polarity: non_inverted 
          function: shift_enable 
          active: high 
          ideal: false 
          user defined: true

    test_mode: 
          object name: TestMode 
          pin name: TestMode 
          hookup_pin: TestMode 
          hookup_polarity: non_inverted 
          function: test_mode 
          active: high 
          ideal: false 
          user defined: true

    test_mode: 
          object name: RST_N 
          pin name: RST_N 
          hookup_pin: RST_N 
          hookup_polarity: non_inverted 
          function: async_set_reset 
          active: low 
          ideal: false 
          user defined: true


Test clock objects
==================
    test_clock:
          object name: ScanClock 
          test_clock_domain: ScanClock 
          user defined: true 
          source: REF_CLK  
          root source: REF_CLK  
          root source polarity: non_inverting
          hookup_pin: REF_CLK 
          period: 20000.0

    test_clock:
          object name: UART_CLK 
          test_clock_domain: UART_CLK 
          user defined: false 
          source: UART_CLK  
          root source: UART_CLK  
          root source polarity: non_inverting
          hookup_pin: UART_CLK 
          period: 50000.0


